## 8. Verification Checklist

After implementation, verify each item before considering this PRD complete:

### Build verification
- [ ] `npm run build` passes with no TypeScript errors
- [ ] `npm run lint` passes with no new warnings

### Behavior verification (local)
- [ ] Visiting `http://localhost:3000` works exactly as before — login, dashboard, all pages function normally
- [ ] The middleware does not break the auth flow: magic link login works, Google OAuth works, the callback at `/auth/callback` works
- [ ] Visiting `/admin/waitlist` still works for platform admins
- [ ] Visiting `/api/cron/daily` with the correct `CRON_SECRET` header still works (middleware is excluded from cron routes)
- [ ] SSE job streams work: click a Refresh button on the dashboard and confirm the job progress bar appears and completes normally
- [ ] Server-side caching is not broken: navigate between dashboard pages and confirm they load correctly

### Header verification
- [ ] Add a temporary `console.log` in a server component to print `headers().get('x-vatic-industry-type')` and confirm it reads `'restaurant'` on localhost
- [ ] Remove the `console.log` before committing

### Middleware exclusion verification
- [ ] Confirm `/_next/static/*` requests do not trigger the middleware (check Vercel function logs or Next.js dev output)
- [ ] Confirm `/api/cron/*` requests do not trigger the middleware

### No regression verification
- [ ] The Playwright smoke test passes: `npm run test:e2e`

